        "highlight_description": "Most brands don't have their own accessories — or they have cheap ones that don't fit well. Euphree designed every bag, basket, and lock to integrate perfectly with your bike. Customers consistently tell us they'd choose a well-accessorized bike over a higher-spec bare one.",
        "highlight_button_label": "Shop All Accessories →",
        "highlight_button_url": "/collections/electric-bike-accessories"
